01:02.832 --> 01:04.632
This could be the best night
of my life,

01:04.700 --> 01:06.234
And I don't want
to have any regrets.

01:06.302 --> 01:08.103
Like when I had the chance
to take ecstasy

01:08.170 --> 01:09.804
At the 2003 tony awards
and didn't.

01:09.872 --> 01:11.339
