(sporadic gunfire,
men screaming)

07:39.765 --> 07:41.332
(sobbing)

07:41.400 --> 07:43.334
(yelling)

07:44.303 --> 07:45.703
Steve, what happened?!

07:45.771 --> 07:47.839
Man, what a letdown.

