08:09.762 --> 08:11.996
Everyone calm down!

08:12.064 --> 08:14.098
I have been in
two war reenactments,

08:14.166 --> 08:16.868
And you men will be safe
if you stick with me.

08:16.935 --> 08:19.120
(screaming)

08:20.469 --> 08:21.269
No!

08:21.337 --> 08:22.305
We gotta get out of here, man.

08:22.306 --> 08:26.306
Let's just go to the snackstop
and get some real cheese, man.

08:26.307 --> 08:28.307
No, we have to save my dad.

08:28.372 --> 08:29.639
I let him down.

08:29.707 --> 08:31.241
Dad, can you hear me?

08:31.309 --> 08:33.743
Steve, it's dark and wet.

08:33.811 --> 08:35.212
There's golf carts.

08:35.279 --> 08:36.679
You have to save...

08:36.746 --> 08:38.715
(man speaking
fake vietnamese)

08:38.783 --> 08:42.152
