the first time!

09:10.281 --> 09:12.082
(speaking vietnamese)

09:14.719 --> 09:16.319
(speaking vietnamese)

09:18.222 --> 09:20.023
Roger, let me go.

09:20.091 --> 09:21.224
(door creaking)

