<i>We were headed up fanangong
river towards gobbley goo bay.</i>

10:18.916 --> 10:23.019
<i>But to get there, we'd have
to go through the 13th fairway.</i>

10:23.087 --> 10:26.089
<i>Freshly fertilized,
we were in the poo.</i>

10:28.326 --> 10:30.126
