10:37.101 --> 10:38.301
My legs!

10:38.369 --> 10:41.104
It blew off my damn legs!

10:41.172 --> 10:42.572
You can make it, buckle!

10:42.640 --> 10:44.441
No, I's done.

10:44.508 --> 10:45.775
Take me out.

10:45.843 --> 10:47.077
I-I can't!

10:47.144 --> 10:50.113
Take the shot!

10:50.181 --> 10:51.281
Not the face!

10:51.349 --> 10:54.050
Oh, my god, that hurt!

10:54.118 --> 10:57.887
Ow! Ow!

10:57.955 --> 11:00.257
Oh, no, it still hurts!

11:00.324 --> 11:01.791
<i>What were we doing here?</i>

11:01.859 --> 11:05.362
<i>Was it worth it
just to become better singers?</i>

11:05.429 --> 11:06.830
<i>The only thing
that made sense anymore</i>

11:06.897 --> 11:10.533
<i>Was my mission: Save dad.</i>

11:10.601 --> 11:13.303
