11:13.371 --> 11:15.505
<i>And I was alone.</i>

11:17.108 --> 11:18.441
<i>In hell.</i>

11:25.850 --> 11:28.585
Damn it!
Stan gave me a fake code!

11:28.653 --> 11:30.687
