11:44.669 --> 11:45.769
Now give me that code.

11:45.836 --> 11:47.103
4812.

11:48.839 --> 11:50.273
4812?!

11:50.341 --> 11:52.642
Wait, he used my pant size?

11:52.710 --> 11:54.377
Ugh, I'm disgusting.

11:55.846 --> 11:58.248
Sorry, hayley, roger tricked me.

11:58.316 --> 12:00.583
